import React from 'react' import './About.css' const About = () => { return(

About Us

Company Mission

Cu-stum's mission is to support people that need that push in ther creative belief. We want to see the decline of people saying I quit in the pursued and pursuing web developers. Cu-stum want web developers to know that no matter what the job lists in there requirements, all they want is someone that love to learn and write code. Cu-stum want web developers to know struggling to learn code is okay.

Team

Cu-stum is a team of web developers that once needed the encouragement that we give you. We are striving to be experts in out tech and leadership.

Jobs

Cu-stum goal is to grow and grow so that we reach the entire world. As of right now we are not hiring but it will be updated on our website as soon as possible. So that's why our hiring application is unavailable.
